# Test back space typing
Output examples/dvds/backspace.svg

Set Width 800
Set Height 400
Set FontSize 16
Set PromptPrefix "\x1b[32m$\x1b[0m "
Set Template macos
Set Theme github-dark
Set Watermark "\x1b[0;2mby talhayut\x1b[0m"

Type "echo 'I am stupid"
Backspace 6
Type "great developer'"
Left 16
Screenshot examples/dvds/backspace_out.svg
Enter
Sleep 100ms
